Dear Mom through the lens of Professional Basketball Player for the Los Angeles Clippers, Terance Mann.

Terance Mann credits his successful basketball career to his mother, who has been his pillar of strength through thick and thin. She has consistently instilled confidence in him and taught him to lead by example with respect. Her guidance and motivation have been instrumental in helping him achieve his dream of playing as a professional athlete for the Los Angeles Clippers. As we celebrate Mother’s Day, we honor the immeasurable impact that mothers have on shaping our lives and providing us with invaluable lessons that guide us along our journey.
#VenusetFleur #dearmom #mothersday
